author: JuliaRegistrator

comments.body: @koehlerson There is already a registered package called [`Gmsh.jl`](https://github.com/JuliaFEM/Gmsh.jl), you can't register a package with the same case-insensitive name.  Note that this would make the register unusable on case-insensitive file systems, which are very common on Windows and macOS systems.
